headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Test Out the Cheval Taipan, Karin Futo GTX, and Invetero Coquette D10
content:
Visit the Test Track located inside of the LS Car Meet to give the Cheval Taipan, Karin Futo GTX, and Invetero Coquette D10 a spin around the columns, challenge your peers to a randomized Scramble, or race against the clock in a Time Trial, without the need to spend any of your savings.

Players can spectate the Test Track inside the LS Car Meet by heading to an exit door of the Test Track and selecting Spectate Test Track.
